text: Mihăiță Vasile Țigănescu (born 4 February 1998) is a Romanian rower. He won the JM4- at the 2016 World Rowing Junior Championships. He won the M4- at 2018 European Rowing Championships. He won a silver medal at the 2019 World Rowing Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for Romania
